{"tid":1507300,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「香港之路」你我他…… - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-08-26T05:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T05:50:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c2eba2be130ad9812aba69da409705fa212e5615","tid":1507300,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:49:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190826/20755790\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190826%2F20755790&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=311baf71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190826%2F20755790&h=a1a6ac49\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190826/20755790</a><br />\n<br />\n「香港之路」你我他&hellip;&hellip; - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190826/large/1566716044_4db3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190826%2Flarge%2F1566716044_4db3.jpg&h=996aa182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8.23「香港之路」的手牽手人鏈活動，效法30年前「波羅的海之路」創舉，和平理性非暴力的示威，當年波羅的海三國200萬人民參加，組成長逾600公里人鏈，橫跨國境連接三國首都，成為宣示團結抗爭的洪流&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n香港民眾借鑑，聚眾集氣。剛結束了狂風暴雨下8.18那170萬人流水式大遊行，這牽手人鏈一樣成功。三線達標還自發延長，看不到盡頭，總路線長達60公里，參與人數逾21萬，影像整晚互傳。表達5大訴求反政警黑暴力，世界各地也有和應，包括波羅的海立陶宛同一時間支持。<br />\n<br />\n人龍中亦有花邊，如示威者不怕風雨也不怕警棍槍彈，但在人鏈中便尷尬不敢主動牽女仔的手（英雄難過美人關）；還有一身聖母像閃亮紅衣的夏蕙姨，兩旁壯男就沒牽她手了（神聖不可侵犯）；收錢展示國旗的在馬路自hi。<br />\n<br />\n人鏈延上獅子山，手機燈光連線，壯觀又感動，配上羅文「&hellip;&hellip;人生不免崎嶇 難以絕無掛慮 既是同舟 在獅子山下且共濟 拋棄區分求共對&hellip;&hellip;同舟人誓相隨 無畏更無懼&hellip;&hellip;」──不必催淚彈，我們自己會流淚。<br />\n<br />\n哥哥的fans傳來他掩着右眼的舊照，同大家一樣甫士，彷彿在遠方為遭黑警射爆眼球失明少女，送上溫暖的鼓勵和支持&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n大家都累了，都被你連累了 (林夕)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n從玄學角度談抗爭 (馮睎乾)<br />\n<br />\n_______________________________<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b783fecff8d877b0b3403ac185a2394959c283","tid":1507300,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:50:47.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=6a0b60ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"d12b2530acc8a575b096f41eed0c8e3c413d87a9","tid":1507300,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:50:48.000Z","msg":"除左春袋，記住：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">九月二~三日 三罷</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">九月二~三日 三罷</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">九月二~三日 三罷</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">九月二~三日 三罷</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">九月二~三日 三罷</span></span><br />\n<span styl